WEBVTT

00:05:58.632 --> 00:06:02.466
and deployed it to protect nature

00:06:02.490 --> 00:06:07.926
from being devoured by the hand
of the global economy.

00:06:07.950 --> 00:06:09.284
It sounded good,

00:06:09.308 --> 00:06:11.537
but in the early '90s in Chile,

00:06:11.561 --> 00:06:15.069
where wildlands philanthropy,
which is what we called it,

00:06:15.093 --> 00:06:17.378
was completely unknown,

00:06:17.402 --> 00:06:20.561
we faced tremendous suspicion,

00:06:20.585 --> 00:06:23.728
and from many quarters,
downright hostility.

00:06:24.101 --> 00:06:28.196
Over time, largely by doing
what we said we were doing,

00:06:28.220 --> 00:06:30.087
we began to win people over.